testTargetEntity.title: Test Target Entity
testTargetEntity.description: Entity to test vision against (usually Player)

playerEntity.title: Player (optional)
playerEntity.description: If not set, the debugger will search for the player automatically.

weaponSystemScriptName.title: Weapon System Script Name
weaponSystemScriptName.description: Script name used on the player (e.g., entity.script.weaponSystem).

cameraEntity.title: Camera (optional)
cameraEntity.description: If not set, the active camera will be detected at runtime.

weaponContainerName.title: Weapon Container Child Name
weaponContainerName.description: Child under the camera that should hold the current weapon model.

targetEntity.title: Target entity (optional)
targetEntity.description: If not set, the debugger tries to locate an entity with healthSystem.

healthScriptName.title: Health script name on the entity

autoAttachListeners.title: Auto-attach verbose listeners for emitted events

enforceSeconds.title: Enforce For (s)
enforceSeconds.description: Keep forcing darkness for this many seconds after initialize.

enforceForever.title: Enforce Forever
enforceForever.description: If true, keep enforcing every frame (useful while debugging).

disableAllLights.title: Disable All Lights
disableAllLights.description: Turn off every Light component in the scene.
